summary:
A medium Nordic tomb east of Whiterun, just a bit southeast from The Ritual Stone.
My first attempt at a Skyrim mod.
descriptionHtml:
A medium Nordic tomb east of Whiterun, just a bit southeast from The Ritual Stone.

Wisgret\'s family is long dead, leaving his tomb abandoned. A small band of renegade mages have moved in, with restless Draugr deeper in the dungeon. Keep an eye out for secrets and treasure, including the journal from one of the current inhabitants.

Radiant Story enabled, should be included in the list of possible generated missions.

Feedback or questions?
sam.combs@gmail.com
author: Sam Combs
